{"kanda":6,"sarga":20,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"ततोनिविष्टांध्वजिनींसुग्रीवेणाभिपालिताम् ।ददर्शराक्षसोऽभ्येत्यशार्दूलोनामवीर्यवान्","trans":"Then the heroic Rakshasa called Shardula entered into the area encamped by the army under Sugriva's command and saw the sign flag of the army.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"वीर्यवान्","m":"heroic one"},{"d":"शार्दूलोनाम:","m":"by name Shardula"},{"d":"राक्षसः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"आभ्येत्य:","m":"entering into"},{"d":"निविष्टाम्","m":"encamped"},{"d":"सुग्रीवेण:","m":"by Sugriva"},{"d":"अभिपालिताम्","m":"under the command of"},{"d":"ध्वजिनीम्","m":"bearing a flag as a mark"},{"d":"ददर्श:","m":"saw."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"चारोराक्षसराजस्यरावणस्यदुरात्मनः ।तांदृष्ट्वासर्वतोव्यग्रंप्रतिगम्यसराक्षसः प्रविश्यलङ्कांवेगेनरावणंवाक्यमब्रवीत् ।","trans":"The evil minded raskshasa who was a spy of Ravana went back to Lanka speedily unruffled after having observed all over the camp and spoke these words to Ravana.","words":[{"d":"दुरात्मनः","m":"evil minded one"},{"d":"राक्षसराजस्य:","m":"Rakshasa kin g's"},{"d":"रावणस्य:","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"चारः","m":"spy"},{"d":"सःराक्षसः","m":"that Rakshasa"},{"d":"अव्यग्रः","m":"not ruffled"},{"d":"ताम्","m":"that"},{"d":"सर्वतः","m":"all over"},{"d":"दृष्टवा:","m":"seeing"},{"d":"प्रतिगम्य:","m":"went back"},{"d":"वेगेन:","m":"speedily"},{"d":"लङ्काम्","m":"to Lanka"},{"d":"प्रविश्य:","m":"entered"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"to Ravana"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"these words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"एषवानरऋक्षौघोलङ्कांसमभिवर्तते ।अगाधश्चाप्रमेयश्चद्वितीयइवसागरः","trans":"As if it is a second ocean deep and immeasurable, the ocean of Vanaras and Bears are heading towards Lanka (reported the spy).","words":[{"d":"द्वितीयः","m":"second"},{"d":"सागरःइव:","m":"like the ocean"},{"d":"अगाधश्च:","m":"deep"},{"d":"आप्रमेयश्च:","m":"and immeasurable"},{"d":"एषः","m":"that way"},{"d":"वानरऋक्षौघः","m":"Vanaras and Bears"},{"d":"लङ्काम्","m":"into Lanka"},{"d":"समभिवर्तते:","m":"are heading towards."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"पुत्रौदशरथस्येमौभ्रातरौरामलक्ष्मणौ उत्तमौरूपसम्पन्नौसीतायाःपदमागतौ ।एतौसागरमासाद्यसन्निविष्टौमहाद्युती","trans":"\"Great sons of Dasaratha, Rama and Lakshmana, endowed with beautiful form and exceptional fortitude have come and set their foot on the seashore and settled to come to Sita.\"","words":[{"d":"दशरथस्य:","m":"Dasaratha's"},{"d":"पुत्रौ:","m":"sons"},{"d":"उत्तमौ:","m":"great"},{"d":"रूपसम्पन्नौ:","m":"endowed with beautiful form"},{"d":"महाद्युती:","m":"exceptional fortitude"},{"d":"भ्रातरौ:","m":"brothers"},{"d":"इमौ:","m":"these"},{"d":"रामलक्ष्मणौ:","m":"Rama and Lakshmana"},{"d":"सीतायाः","m":"Sita's"},{"d":"पदम्","m":"to set foot"},{"d":"आगतौ:","m":"have come"},{"d":"सागरम्","m":"sea"},{"d":"आसाद्य:","m":"reached"},{"d":"सन्निविष्टौ:","m":"settled."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"पुत्रौदशरथस्येमौभ्रातरौरामलक्ष्मणौ उत्तमौरूपसम्पन्नौसीतायाःपदमागतौ ।एतौसागरमासाद्यसन्निविष्टौमहाद्युती","trans":"\"Great sons of Dasaratha, Rama and Lakshmana, endowed with beautiful form and exceptional fortitude have come and set their foot on the seashore and settled to come to Sita.\"","words":[{"d":"दशरथस्य:","m":"Dasaratha's"},{"d":"पुत्रौ:","m":"sons"},{"d":"उत्तमौ:","m":"great"},{"d":"रूपसम्पन्नौ:","m":"endowed with beautiful form"},{"d":"महाद्युती:","m":"exceptional fortitude"},{"d":"भ्रातरौ:","m":"brothers"},{"d":"इमौ:","m":"these"},{"d":"रामलक्ष्मणौ:","m":"Rama and Lakshmana"},{"d":"सीतायाः","m":"Sita's"},{"d":"पदम्","m":"to set foot"},{"d":"आगतौ:","m":"have come"},{"d":"सागरम्","m":"sea"},{"d":"आसाद्य:","m":"reached"},{"d":"सन्निविष्टौ:","m":"settled."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"बलंचामाकाशमावृत्यसर्वतोदशयोजनम् ।तत्त्वभूतंमहाराज क्षिप्रंवेदितुमर्हसि","trans":"\"Mighty king Ravana the army also is spread all over ten yojanas. I have seen going round the sky. You ought to know the real situation at once.\"","words":[{"d":"महाराज:","m":"O king"},{"d":"बलंच:","m":"army also"},{"d":"सर्वतः","m":"all over"},{"d":"दशयोजनम्","m":"ten yojanas"},{"d":"आयतम्","m":"spread"},{"d":"आकाशम्","m":"sky"},{"d":"आवृत्य:","m":"going round"},{"d":"तत्त्वभूतम्","m":"real situation"},{"d":"क्षिप्रम्","m":"at once"},{"d":"वेदितुम्","m":"should know"},{"d":"अर्हसि:","m":"you ought to."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"तवदूतामहाराजक्षिप्रमर्हन्त्यवेक्षितुम् ।उपप्रदानंसान्त्वंवाभेदोवात्रप्रयुज्यताम्","trans":"\"O king at once your spies should be deployed there and entrusted to have claims either by conciliation or creating differences.\"","words":[{"d":"महाराज:","m":"O king"},{"d":"तव:","m":"your"},{"d":"दूताः","m":"spies"},{"d":"क्षिप्रम्","m":"at once"},{"d":"अवेक्षितुम्","m":"seeing"},{"d":"अर्हन्ति:","m":"having a claim"},{"d":"उपप्रदानम्","m":"entrusting"},{"d":"सान्त्वंवा:","m":"by conciliation"},{"d":"भेदोवा:","m":"by creating difference"},{"d":"अत्रप्रयुज्यताम्","m":"to be deployed there."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"शार्दूलस्यवचश्श्रुत्वारावणोराक्षसेश्वरः ।उवाचसहसाव्यग्रस्सम्प्रधार्यार्थमात्मनः शुकंनामतदारक्षोवाक्यमर्थविदांवरम् ।","trans":"Ravana the tiger among Rakshasas, after having heard Shardula's words decided within himself and said to Suka who is good at work praising him very much as usual.","words":[{"d":"राक्षसेश्वरः","m":"Lord of Rakshasas"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"शार्दूलस्य:","m":"Shardula's"},{"d":"वचः","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा:","m":"on hearing"},{"d":"सहसा:","m":"rashly"},{"d":"व्यग्रः","m":"disturbed"},{"d":"आत्मनः","m":"own self"},{"d":"अर्थम्","m":"What to do"},{"d":"सम्प्रधार्य:","m":"as usual"},{"d":"तदा:","m":"then"},{"d":"अर्थविदाम्","m":"praising"},{"d":"वरम्","m":"supreme"},{"d":"शुकंनाम:","m":"called Suka"},{"d":"रक्षः","m":"to protect"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"these words"},{"d":"उवाच:","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"सुग्रीवंब्रूहिगत्वाशुराजानंवचनान्मम ।यथासन्देशमक्लीबंश्लक्ष्णयापरयागिरा","trans":"\"Departing quickly, speak to the king Sugriva boldly without getting disturbed but in a gentle way and communicate this message.\"","words":[{"d":"राजानम्","m":"to the king"},{"d":"सुग्रीवम्","m":"to Sugriva"},{"d":"आशु:","m":"fast"},{"d":"गत्वा:","m":"approaching"},{"d":"मम:","m":"my"},{"d":"वचनात्","m":"words"},{"d":"यथासन्देशम्","m":"this message"},{"d":"परया:","m":"stranger"},{"d":"श्लक्ष्णया:","m":"gently"},{"d":"गिरा","m":"speaking"},{"d":"अक्लीबम्","m":"without getting disturbed"},{"d":"ब्रूहि:","m":"to speak."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"त्वंवैमहाराजकुलप्रसूतोमहाबलश्चर् क्षरजस्सुतश्च ।नकश्चिदार्थस्तवनास्त्यनर्थस्तथाहिमेभ्रातृसमोहरीश","trans":"\"O Sugriva, king of Vanaras You are born in a race of eminent kings, a mighty son of Rksharaja. Even a little harm has not been done to you by me. I am like your brother (Ravana's words to Sugriva to be communicated by Suka).\"","words":[{"d":"महाराज:","m":"O king"},{"d":"हरीश:","m":"Vanara"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"your"},{"d":"कुलप्रसूतःवै:","m":"eminent kings"},{"d":"महाबलश्च:","m":"mighty strong"},{"d":"ऋक्षरजस्सुतश्च:","m":"and Rksharaja's son"},{"d":"तव:","m":"your"},{"d":"अर्थः","m":"meaning"},{"d":"कश्चन:","m":"a little"},{"d":"नास्ति:","m":"not"},{"d":"अनर्थः","m":"harm"},{"d":"न:","m":"not"},{"d":"तथापि:","m":"so also"},{"d":"मे:","m":"I am"},{"d":"भ्रातृसमः","m":"like your brother."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"अहंयद्यहरंभार्यांराजपुत्रस्यधीमतः ।किंतत्रतवसुग्रीव: किष्किन्धांप्रतिगम्यताम्","trans":"\"Sugriva What harm is done to you if I have brought the consort of prince? You are a wise one, go back to Kishkinda.\"","words":[{"d":"सुग्रीव:","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"धीमतः","m":"wise one"},{"d":"राजपुत्रस्य:","m":"prince's"},{"d":"भार्याम्","m":"consort"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"अहरंयदि:","m":"even if I have brought away also"},{"d":"तत्र:","m":"there"},{"d":"तव:","m":"your"},{"d":"किम्","m":"what"},{"d":"किष्किन्धांप्रति:","m":"return to Kishkinda"},{"d":"गम्यताम्","m":"to reach."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"नहीयंहरिभिर्लङ्काशक्याप्राप्तुंकथञ्चन ।देवैरपिसगन्धर्वैःकिंपुनर्नरवानरैः","trans":"\"It is not possible for Vanaras to get here even for Gandharvas or Devas also. What to say of humans and Vanaras? (You may tell this to Sugriva).\"","words":[{"d":"इयंलङ्का:","m":"in this Lanka"},{"d":"हरिभिः","m":"even Vanaras"},{"d":"प्राप्तुम्","m":"to get here"},{"d":"नशक्याहि:","m":"is not possible"},{"d":"सगन्धर्वैः","m":"even Gandharvas"},{"d":"देवैरपि:","m":"even Devas also"},{"d":"नरवानरैः","m":"of humans and Vanaras"},{"d":"किंपुनः","m":"what to say."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"सतथाराक्षसेन्द्रेणसन्दिष्टोरजनीचरः ।शुकोविहङ्गमोभूत्वातूर्णमाप्लुत्यचाम्बरम्","trans":"Thus, commanded by the ruler of Rakshasas, Suka immediately transformed into a bird form and rose apace into the sky.","words":[{"d":"तथा:","m":"so"},{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्रे:","m":"ruler of Rakshasas"},{"d":"सन्दिष्टः","m":"commanded thus"},{"d":"सः","m":"that"},{"d":"शुकः","m":"Suka"},{"d":"विहङ्गमः","m":"bird"},{"d":"भूत्वा:","m":"transforming"},{"d":"अम्बरम्","m":"sky"},{"d":"तूर्णम्","m":"immediately"},{"d":"आप्लुत्यच:","m":"rose apace into."}]},{"v":14,"dev":"सगत्वादूरमध्वानमुपर्युपरिसागरम् ।संस्थितोह्यम्बरेवाक्यंसुग्रीवमिदमब्रवीत्","trans":"Suka having gone a long way in the sky to a distant place, stationed there spoke these words to Sugriva.","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he (Suka)"},{"d":"सागरम्","m":"ocean"},{"d":"दूरम्","m":"long way"},{"d":"अध्वानम्","m":"having distant space"},{"d":"गत्वा:","m":"gone"},{"d":"अम्बरे:","m":"in the sky"},{"d":"संस्थितः","m":"stationed"},{"d":"सुग्रीवम्","m":"to Sugriva"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"these"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"सर्वमुक्तंयथादिष्टंरावणेनदुरात्मना ।तंप्रापयन्तंवचनंतूर्णमाप्लुत्यवानराः प्रापद्यन्तदिवंक्षिप्रंलोप्तुंहन्तुंचमुष्टिभि: ।","trans":"Thus, commanded by evil minded Ravana, Suka communicated everything as spoken by Ravana. At once the Vanaras rose and started to injure Suka with their fists.","words":[{"d":"दुरात्मना:","m":"evil minded one"},{"d":"रावणेन:","m":"by Ravana"},{"d":"यथा:","m":"thus"},{"d":"आदिष्टम्","m":"commanded"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"everything"},{"d":"उक्तम्","m":"spoke"},{"d":"तम्","m":"his"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"प्रापयन्तम्","m":"while communicating"},{"d":"वान